<p class="">Would the hon Member go on to say that the right thing to do is for him to make his contribution to the Treasury, and for everyone else to make their contributions to the Treasury, and then ask the Treasury to feed us all?</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
