<p class="">Does the hon. Member suggest that it can be given back only in the form of Income Tax? Could it not be given back in indirect taxation?</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-b5ebd06c-85c9-41f8-a8d7-330ec748e9e9" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
