<p class="">Is the hon. Gentleman seriously describing all those members of the public who have bought Savings Certificates on the Chancellor's advice as robbers?</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-4c437cbe-c7eb-45f1-93eb-b1e6a129b77a" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
